      "id": "9adffdf1_2af6aaf9",
      "file_path": "ansible/docker/build_ansible_image.sh",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 30,
      "message": "N/A is universally known as Not Applicable, it can confuse an automatic tool about the same as that commit ref, but removing this label completely can confuse already existing automatic tool - in another words - existing environment is unaffected - this change only brings new usage outside of the git repo - if the label has no real usage and actually breaks something it can be removed in the future - as of now this change only improves user experience",
